----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Replication Controller (old) :
  - Helps running mutliple instanaces of single pod thus proivdes Replication Controller
  -  For load Balancing and scaling 

Replica Set(new) : 
 - Selectors is mandatpry in Replica set 
 - Selectors helps identify what pods under it, can also manage pods created before or exisitng pods.

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Deployments: 

  - Used for Upgrades 
  - Rolling Updates 
  - Provides capbalities to upgarde pods and uses rolling updates. 
  - It is layer above replicaset.
  - So a Deployments creates replicaset for maintaing pods 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Namespaces: helps in isolating environents 

